Grab asv table from a tsv file and format to tibble

asv_data_tsv.Rd

Grab asv table from a tsv file and format to tibble

Usage

asv_data_tsv(tsv)

Arguments

tsv

A character vector specifying the path to seqtab.tsv

Value

A tibble.

Examples

fpath <- system.file("extdata/tsv", "seqtab.tsv", package = "bubbler")
asv_data_tsv(fpath)
